ack and Field competition isstreaming live on FloTrack, MileSplit and the FloSports app.Highlights, replays and breaking news are on both platforms.\", \"from\": 714, \"to\": 889, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 723, \"end\": 738, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AAU_Junior_Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Junior Olympics\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AAU_Junior_Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AAU_Junior_Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 815, \"end\": 824, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FloSports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"FloSports\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FloSports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FloSports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not miss all the track and field season action streaming on FloTrack.Check out the FloTrack schedule for more events.\", \"from\": 891, \"to\": 1011, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Video footage from each event will be archived and stored in a video library for FloTrack subscribers to watch for the duration of their subscriptions.\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1164, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tags:  Get the most important Track & Field stories delivered straight to your inbox.\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1251, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1196, \"end\": 1209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Track_and_field\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6026536076039625e-33, \"text\": \"Track & Field\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Track_and_field\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Track_and_field\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a92006 - Present FloSports, Inc. All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 1253, \"to\": 1305, \"entities\": []}]}"